# 預測

## 模型位置
from fastai.vision.all import *
myPath='/content/drive/MyDrive/myclass2021/models'
myModel=myPath+'/nodule_finetune.pkl'
learn = load_learner(myModel)


## 執行預測
fnames_normal=get_image_files('/content/dataset/test/normal/')
fnames_nodule=get_image_files('/content/dataset/test/nodule')
pred_class,pred_idx,outputs = learn.predict(fnames_normal[3])
print("Actual: Normal, Predicted = {}".format(pred_class))
pred_class,pred_idx,outputs = learn.predict(fnames_nodule[7])
print("Actual: Pneumonia, Predicted = {}".format(pred_class))

Actual: Normal, Predicted = normal

Actual: Pneumonia, Predicted = nodule
